text: Taourirt is a village in northern Algeria. It is located in Bouïra Province. Nearby towns and villages include Tassift (3.0 nm), M'Chedallah(3.1 nm), Chorfa (2.6 nm), Boudjellil (1.9 nm) and Sidi Brahim (5.9 nm).Falling rain gazetteer The place is located along the N5 road which leads to Adjiba. ==References== ==External links== *Satellite map at Maplandia.com Category:Populated places in Bouïra Province Category:Villages in Algeria
title: Taourirt, Algeria
